<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>随笔 on 编程心语</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/tags/%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/</link><description>Recent content in 随笔 on 编程心语</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 08:32:30 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ithome.me/tags/%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>不敢裸辞的全栈开发者</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/afraid-to-quit/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/afraid-to-quit/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img
 class="lazyload"
 src="https://www.ithome.me/svg/loading.min.svg"
 data-src="https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/afraid-to-quit/featured.jpg"
 data-srcset="https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/afraid-to-quit/featured.jpg, https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/afraid-to-quit/featured.jpg 1.5x, https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/afraid-to-quit/featured.jpg 2x"
 data-sizes="auto"
 alt="/post/2026/07/17/afraid-to-quit/featured.jpg"
 title="深夜办公桌上亮着代码编辑器的屏幕" width="1059" height="556" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;凌晨十一点半，改完最后一个bug，合上电脑。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;手机弹了一条消息，前同事发了条朋友圈：「裸辞了，去大理gap一个月。」&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我点了个赞，然后躺床上翻来覆去睡不着。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>囤书焦虑：我的书架上有192本书，我只读完了2本</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/bookshelf-guilt/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/bookshelf-guilt/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img
 class="lazyload"
 src="https://www.ithome.me/svg/loading.min.svg"
 data-src="https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/bookshelf-guilt/featured.jpg"
 data-srcset="https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/bookshelf-guilt/featured.jpg, https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/bookshelf-guilt/featured.jpg 1.5x, https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/bookshelf-guilt/featured.jpg 2x"
 data-sizes="auto"
 alt="/post/2026/07/17/bookshelf-guilt/featured.jpg"
 title="书架上堆满未拆封的书" width="1059" height="556" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;前几天整理微信读书书架，数了一下：192本。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;读完的：2本。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;一本是《蚂蚁金服》，一本是《结构性改革》。两本都是出差坐高铁时看完的——因为在高铁上没有别的事可做，没有WiFi，没有消息弹窗，没有「再刷五分钟手机就睡觉」。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>程序员也配点25块的外卖？</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/programmer-25-yuan-delivery/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 15:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/programmer-25-yuan-delivery/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img
 class="lazyload"
 src="https://www.ithome.me/svg/loading.min.svg"
 data-src="https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/programmer-25-yuan-delivery/featured.jpg"
 data-srcset="https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/programmer-25-yuan-delivery/featured.jpg, https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/programmer-25-yuan-delivery/featured.jpg 1.5x, https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/programmer-25-yuan-delivery/featured.jpg 2x"
 data-sizes="auto"
 alt="/post/2026/07/17/programmer-25-yuan-delivery/featured.jpg"
 title="外卖配送员和程序员的日常" width="1059" height="556" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;又是一个阳光灿烂的中午，刷了一上午的 GitHub Trending，咖啡也灌了好几杯，肚子早已经咕咕作响了。今天中午吃点什么呢，打开外卖 App 翻了翻，公司楼下新开了一家轻食沙拉，满减后 25 块，看起来还不错。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;就在我准备下单的时候，余光瞥到了旁边工位的老王。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;老王正偷偷摸摸打开同一家店，手指悬在「25 元烟熏鸡胸肉沙拉」上面，犹豫着要不要点。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我认出了他。发际线已经退到了头顶三分之二的位置，颈贴从衣领里露出一角，保温杯里泡着枸杞和菊花，屏幕上开着一堆 Terminal——这些特征都在大声宣告他的身份：&lt;strong&gt;一个 2026 年的程序员。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我默默地转过头去，用犀利的眼神和他做着底层通信。我传达的信息很明确：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;你，也配点 25 块的外卖？&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>鱼缸碎碎念：一个懒人新手的养鱼日记</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/fish-tank-lazy-diary/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/fish-tank-lazy-diary/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img
 class="lazyload"
 src="https://www.ithome.me/svg/loading.min.svg"
 data-src="https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/fish-tank-lazy-diary/featured.jpg"
 data-srcset="https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/fish-tank-lazy-diary/featured.jpg, https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/fish-tank-lazy-diary/featured.jpg 1.5x, https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/17/fish-tank-lazy-diary/featured.jpg 2x"
 data-sizes="auto"
 alt="/post/2026/07/17/fish-tank-lazy-diary/featured.jpg"
 title="20加仑鱼缸里色彩斑斓的小鱼" width="1059" height="556" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;事情要从那个20加仑的鱼缸说起。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="为什么养鱼"&gt;为什么养鱼&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;说实话，养鱼不是我的第一选择。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;先是养猫，老婆嫌掉毛。养狗，出差没人管。养乌龟，查了一圈发现可能比我活得还久，到时候谁送谁走还不一定。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>从头来过</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2013/03/03/%E4%BB%8E%E5%A4%B4%E6%9D%A5%E8%BF%87/</link><pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2013 15:31:09 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2013/03/03/%E4%BB%8E%E5%A4%B4%E6%9D%A5%E8%BF%87/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;我勒个去，两年的心血啊，文章全丢了。从头来过，好好写文章！&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>